AVCAssistant(8)              System Manager's Manual             AVCAssistant(8)

NAME
     AVCAssistant â€“ CoreMediaIO DAL Assistant Process.

DESCRIPTION
     AVCAssistant is used by the CoreMediaIO Device Abstraction Layer Plug-In
     that provides audio/video capture from FireWire (IEEE 1394) AVC-class
     devices (DV and HDV cameras and decks) using AVFoundation Capture APIs.
     The process allows multiple applications to simultaneously capture from the
     same AVC device.

